## Source of Truth

- Combat logic: `backend/src/lib/game/combat.ts`
- Balance formulas: `backend/src/lib/game/balance.ts`
- Live config: `backend/src/lib/game/live-config.ts`
- Detailed doc: `docs/06_game_systems/COMBAT.md`
- Constants: `docs/06_game_systems/BALANCE_CONSTANTS.md`

## Server-Authoritative Rule (CRITICAL)

Клиент НЕ СЧИТАЕТ: результаты боя, награды, рейтинг, экономические значения. Отображай то, что прислал сервер.

## Combat Flow

1. Client запрашивает бой → Server находит оппонента (matchmaking)
2. Server выполняет `runCombat()` (async!) → generates seeded RNG log
3. Server обновляет ELO, выдаёт rewards, degradation
4. Client получает результат + combat log для replay

## Matchmaking (updated 2026-03-23)

- ±10 уровней, ±80% gear score
- 3-phase cascade fallback (tight → medium → wide)
- Starting rating: 1000, calibration phase

## Stance System

- Attack zone (head/chest/legs) + Defense zone (head/chest/legs)
- Zone matching: +15% DEF при match, +5% OFF при miss
- UI: `StanceDisplayView` (отдельный компонент)
- Selector: `StanceSelectorDetailView`
- Bonus data: `StanceSelectorViewModel.attackBonuses(for:)`, `defenseBonuses(for:)`

## Arena Screen Layout

- Sticky title + tabs (OPPONENTS / REVENGE / HISTORY) pinned above ScrollView
- Content: ActiveQuestBanner → UnifiedHeroWidget → PvP Stats → LowHP → Stance → Tab content
- Refresh button pinned to bottom (opponents tab only)

## PvP Data Models

- `PvPRank` — НЕТ `.displayName`, используй `.rawValue`
- `LeaderboardEntry` — `.characterClass` это String, не enum. Конвертируй: `CharacterClass(rawValue:) ?? .warrior`
- `OpponentProfile` — full public profile для PvP sheet
- `ItemRarity.color` — computed property для rarity-colored borders

## Revenge System

- 72-hour expiration
- Tracked in `pvp/revenge/[id]` route
- Badge in arena tab

## Achievement Tracking

- 9 PvP achievements tracked in `pvp/fight`, `pvp/resolve`, `pvp/revenge/[id]`
- 4 ranking achievements tracked after ELO update
- `absolute: true` for streaks and ratings

## Damage Type Enum

`physical`, `magical`, `true_damage`, `poison` — не придумывай других.
